description: Lists all the versions of the templates in the current Amazon QuickSight account.

parameters.name: AwsAccountId
parameters.description: The ID of the Amazon Web Services account that contains the templates that you're listing.

nested_items.name: TemplateVersionSummaryList
nested_items.description: A structure containing a list of all the versions of the specified template.

nested_items.name: Arn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the template version.

nested_items.name: VersionNumber
nested_items.description: The version number of the template version.

nested_items.name: CreatedTime
nested_items.description: The time that this template version was created.

nested_items.name: Status
nested_items.description: The status of the template version.

nested_items.name: Description
nested_items.description: The description of the template version.

nested_items.name: NextToken
nested_items.description: The token for the next set of results, or null if there are no more results.

nested_items.name: Status
nested_items.description: The HTTP status of the request.

nested_items.name: RequestId
nested_items.description: The Amazon Web Services request ID for this operation.
